_Feel_ the difference? Now that you've _flattened_ the _bottom_, it _can't roll_ on you. And it's time to _combine_ our _two techniques_. Use your _knife hand_ to _slice_ while your _claw hand_ holds the _carrot still_ on the board, _gradually feeding_ it into the knife as you slice.

